2.1 Proposed System
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
lettrine{I}{n }
\end_layout

\end_inset

order to reach the scope, i will proposed a system with an interface develop
 both for web and smart device.
 Users will open the app and then they will choose what is their necessity
 : traffic situation, emergency or parking for example.
 Registration is not mandatory but it is strongly raccomended in order to
 be able to use all functionalities: for example, general notification could
 be recived only by registred users.
 With respect to the necessity to recive information, for example, about
 best way to do, will be necessary an internet connection.
 The system will interact with users directly via notification, via monitor
 (that are posed in the main streets) and, indirectly, with the management
 of traffic lights.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section*
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
addcontentsline{toc}{section}{2.2 Assumptions}
\end_layout

\end_inset

2.2 Assumptions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
lettrine{C}{oherently }
\end_layout

\end_inset

with specification document, is necessary to do some assumption in order
 to increase the clarity:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A1] We assume that every user has a smartphone if he/se want use the app;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A2] We assume that every user has a internet connection;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A3] We assume that each citizen will follow the instructions provided by
 application;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A4] We assume that special situation (as manifestation or VIP's visit)
 will be scheduled in advace;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A5] We assume that in case of accidents, they will be notify as soon as
 possible;
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A6] We assume that when an accident happen, someone will call hospital
 or police and in that moment the first structure that will recive the help
 request will also insert it in the system, manually or by an automatic
 system
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A7] We assume that all hospital structure, all police stations, all car
 parks and the public transport company will answer in a positive way to
 this innovative solution
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A8] We assume that Administration has created an organization in order
 to keeping on work each sensor and actuator in the city
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[A9] We assume that after the period indicated fot a scheduled event, system
 will deleted it automatically.
 On the DB will be manteined a documentation about all passed events
\end_layout

