4.1.3.3 Parking Availability
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R1] Car Parks in the city must be complitely automated
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R2] Some actuator will releve the availability or not availability in a
 fixed car park.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R3] The situation will be update in the system each time that actuators
 will detect somethings.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R4] In case of reservation, system will be implementing for using QR code.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R5] Each User that will reserve a place will recive a QR code that he/she
 must show when he/she will arrive to the car park
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R6] In each car park there will be a QR reader, near the entry 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
[R7] The QR will be valid coherently with the time indicate for the reservation
 (five, ten, fifteen...)
\end_layout

